00:40:00.510 --> 00:40:01.850 align:middle line:84%
I've had so much fun
with you, George.

00:40:01.850 --> 00:40:03.558 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You know, as
we've talked about,

00:40:03.558 --> 00:40:07.400 align:middle line:84%
